sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant WebAPI as Web API Container
    participant JWT as JWT Auth Handler
    participant Semantic as Semantic Layer
    participant Blockchain as Blockchain Core
    participant RDFStore as RDF Store
    participant Pool as Transaction Pool
    participant Consensus as Consensus Engine
    participant P2P as P2P Network

    Note over Client,P2P: Transaction Submission Flow

    Client->>WebAPI: POST /api/transactions<br/>(RDF Turtle data)
    activate WebAPI

    WebAPI->>JWT: Validate JWT Token
    activate JWT
    JWT-->>WebAPI: Token Valid (User: supply_chain_mgr)
    deactivate JWT

    WebAPI->>Semantic: Validate RDF with SHACL
    activate Semantic
    Semantic->>RDFStore: Load Ontology Shapes
    activate RDFStore
    RDFStore-->>Semantic: SHACL Shapes Loaded
    deactivate RDFStore

    Semantic->>Semantic: Check Constraints
    Semantic-->>WebAPI: Validation Passed ✅
    deactivate Semantic

    WebAPI->>Blockchain: Add Transaction to Pool
    activate Blockchain
    Blockchain->>Pool: Store Pending Transaction
    activate Pool
    Pool-->>Blockchain: Transaction Queued
    deactivate Pool

    Note over Blockchain,P2P: Block Creation (1 second interval)

    Blockchain->>Pool: Get Pending Transactions
    activate Pool
    Pool-->>Blockchain: Return 100 Transactions
    deactivate Pool

    Blockchain->>Blockchain: Create Block
    Note right of Blockchain: - Assemble transactions<br/>- Calculate Merkle root<br/>- Set timestamp

    Blockchain->>Blockchain: Sign Block (Ed25519)
    Note right of Blockchain: Validator public key:<br/>0xabc123...

    Blockchain->>Consensus: Broadcast Proposed Block
    activate Consensus

    par Collect Votes from Peers
        Consensus->>P2P: Broadcast to Peer 1
        P2P-->>Consensus: Vote: APPROVE
        and
        Consensus->>P2P: Broadcast to Peer 2
        P2P-->>Consensus: Vote: APPROVE
        and
        Consensus->>P2P: Broadcast to Peer 3
        P2P-->>Consensus: Vote: APPROVE
    end

    Consensus-->>Blockchain: Consensus Reached (3/3)
    deactivate Consensus

    Blockchain->>RDFStore: Persist Block Triples
    activate RDFStore
    Note right of RDFStore: Graph: http://provchain.org/block/42
    RDFStore-->>Blockchain: Triples Persisted (250 triples)
    deactivate RDFStore

    Blockchain-->>WebAPI: Block Created ✅<br/>Hash: 0xdef456...
    deactivate Blockchain

    WebAPI-->>Client: 201 Created<br/>Block: 42, Hash: 0xdef456...
    deactivate WebAPI

    Note over Client,P2P: SPARQL Query Flow

    Client->>WebAPI: POST /api/query<br/>(SPARQL SELECT query)
    activate WebAPI

    WebAPI->>JWT: Validate JWT Token
    JWT-->>WebAPI: Token Valid

    WebAPI->>Semantic: Execute SPARQL with OWL2 Reasoning
    activate Semantic

    Semantic->>RDFStore: Load Ontology
    activate RDFStore
    RDFStore-->>Semantic: Ontology Loaded
    deactivate RDFStore

    Semantic->>Semantic: Apply Tableaux Reasoning
    Note right of Semantic: Property chains,<br/>Qualified cardinality

    Semantic->>RDFStore: Execute SPARQL
    activate RDFStore
    RDFStore-->>Semantic: Query Results
    deactivate RDFStore

    Semantic-->>WebAPI: Results (5 product traceability records)
    deactivate Semantic

    WebAPI-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>JSON Results
    deactivate WebAPI
